Package: neurotabs
Type: Package
Title: Neuro Feature Tables - Storage-Independent Neuroimaging Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Brad", "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Reference implementation of the NFTab specification for
    row-oriented neuroimaging datasets. Read, write, validate, and query
    collections of neuroimaging observations with design metadata and
    feature values that resolve to logical arrays (volumes, ROI vectors,
    surfaces) independent of physical storage backend.
